'''理查德·H·塞勒'''（{{lang-en|Richard H. Thaler}}，{{IPAc-en|ˈ|θ|eɪ|l|ər}}；{{bd|1945年|9月12日|||}}）是一位美国经济学家、[[芝加哥大学|芝加哥大学]]布思商业学院拉尔夫和多萝西凯勒杰出服务教授。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Home|url=https://faculty.chicagobooth.edu/Richard.Thaler/index.html|accessdate=2019-09-06|work=faculty.chicagobooth.edu|archive-date=2021-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303034118/https://faculty.chicagobooth.edu/richard.thaler/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他是[[行为金融学|行为金融学]]的最知名的理论家之一。由於他在[[行為經濟學|行為經濟學]]的卓越貢獻<ref>{{cite news | last = Appelbaum | first = Binyamin | title = Nobel in Economics Is Awarded to Richard Thaler | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 2017-10-09 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2017/10/09/business/nobel-economics-richard-thaler.html | accessdate = 2017-10-09 | archive-date = 2020-05-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200519021631/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/10/09/business/nobel-economics-richard-thaler.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，因此獲得2017年[[諾貝爾經濟學獎|諾貝爾經濟學獎]]<ref>{{cite news | last = Tetlow | first = Gemma | title = Richard Thaler awarded 2017 Nobel prize in economics | newspaper = Financial Times | date = 2017-10-09 | url = https://www.ft.com/content/49f68431-8675-3a0c-ab51-b90c230ed2ba | accessdate = 2017-10-09 | archive-date = 2020-02-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200219025240/https://www.ft.com/content/49f68431-8675-3a0c-ab51-b90c230ed2ba | dead-url = no }}</ref>。
