== 生平 ==
1945年生于美国{{le|新泽西州东奥兰治|East Orange, New Jersey}}，他是Fuller & Thaler[[资产管理|资产管理]]公司的创始人之一。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fullerthaler.com/|publisher=Fuller & Thaler Asset Management|title=Behavioral Investing|access-date=October 11, 2017|archive-date=2017-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171009195406/https://www.fullerthaler.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 该公司拥有一批会利用如[[禀赋效应|禀赋效应]]、[[损失规避|损失规避]]和[[现状偏差|现状偏差]]等[[認知偏誤|認知偏誤]]的投资者，其中有2位诺贝尔奖获得者。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fullerthaler.com/ |publisher=Fuller & Thaler Asset Management |title=About Us |access-date=October 11, 2017 |archive-date=2017-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171009195406/https://www.fullerthaler.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

塞勒在電影《[[大賣空_(電影)|大賣空]]》（2015年）中饰演自己，和[[赛琳娜·戈麦斯|赛琳娜·戈麦斯]]一起解释[[熱手謬誤|熱手謬誤]]。<ref name="Wired">{{cite web|first=Angela|last=Watercutter|url=https://www.wired.com/2015/12/big-short-understanding-economics|title=The Big Short Somehow Makes Subprime Mortgages Entertaining|publisher=Wired.com|date=December 11, 2015|accessdate=October 10, 2017|archive-date=2017-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010102356/https://www.wired.com/2015/12/big-short-understanding-economics/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

